title: Episode #57 - Jen Kirkman & ME
description: Stand-up Comedian, Author, Actress, Chelsea Lately regular, & host of the podcast I SEEM FUN...Jen Kirkman joins me in the Mancave to talk about our past beef, twitter wars, flight anxiety, & life w/ or without kids.
